OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FThree prisoners accused of murdering a
OL,7,Fchild killer and leaving him "tucked
OL,8,Fup in bed" have never provided an
OL,9,Fexplanation of what happened in the
OL,10,Fcell "because they can't", prosecutors
OL,11,Fhave told a jury.
OL,13,FInmates Mark Fellows, 45, Lee Newell,
OL,14,F57, and David Taylor, 64, are accused
OL,15,Fof murdering 33-year-old Kyle Bevan at
OL,16,Fhigh-security HMP Wakefield in West
OL,17,FYorkshire on November 4 last year.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@JO]rD@FOUrD@YO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
