FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FBevan was serving a life sentence with
OL,7,Fa minimum tariff of 28 years for
OL,8,Fmurdering his partner's two-year-old
OL,9,Fdaughter, Lola James, in
OL,10,FHaverfordwest, Pembrokeshire, in 2020.
OL,12,FProsecutors say the three defendants
OL,13,Fwere seen on CCTV going into his cell
OL,14,Fand emerging less than five minutes
OL,15,Flater.
OL,17,FBevan was put in his bed after the
OL,18,Fattack and was not discovered until
OL,19,Fthe following morning when it was
OL,20,Ffound he had bled to death after
OL,21,Fsuffering 25 stab wounds.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FThe three defendants have all chosen
OL,7,Fnot to give evidence in their trial at
OL,8,FLeeds Crown Court.
OL,10,FGiving his closing speech to jurors on
OL,11,FWednesday, prosecutor Jason Pitter KC
OL,12,Fsaid: "None of them has taken the
OL,13,Fopportunity to explain to you, to the
OL,14,Fcourt, to the police at any stage,
OL,15,Fwhat happened. We say, that's because
OL,16,Fthey can't."
OL,26,@tD@GOUxD@LO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FMr Pitter said the killing of Bevan
OL,7,Fwas a "carefully coordinated venture
OL,8,Fcarried out with real efficiency by
OL,9,Fpeople who ... knew what they were
OL,10,Fdoing".
OL,12,FHe said they left him "tidily tucked
OL,13,Fup in bed ... as he bled out on his
OL,14,Fmattress, looking like, to all intents
OL,15,Fand purposes, as if he was asleep".
OL,17,FHe told jurors the attack took place
OL,18,Fin "four minutes and 39 seconds when
OL,19,Fall three of them were in that tiny
OL,20,Fcell together".
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@FO]tD@WOUwD@bO]zD@DOU|D@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FThe prosecutor said that, as Taylor
OL,7,Fwas transferred out of Wakefield, he
OL,8,Fwas heard to shout towards Newell
OL,9,F"nice working with you and the Iceman"
OL,10,F` a nickname for Fellows.
OL,12,FHe told the court those words showed
OL,13,FTaylor "could not have been more proud
OL,14,Fof the work ... they had done
OL,15,Ftogether".
OL,17,FThe trial has heard that, unlike other
OL,18,Fprisons, vulnerable prisoners were not
OL,19,Fseparated from other inmates at HMP
OL,20,FWakefield.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@fO]uD@HOUwD@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
