PN,33606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FMr Pitter said the regime meant that
OL,7,Fthe three defendants "had to mix with,
OL,8,Fin a distorted moral hierarchy, other
OL,9,Fcriminals that were beneath them".
OL,11,FHe said the defendants had a hostility
OL,12,Fto people who had committed offences
OL,13,Fagainst children, and Fellows and
OL,14,FNewell had expressed a desire to move
OL,15,Faway.
OL,26,@oD@VOUqD@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FMr Pitter told jurors that Fellows had
OL,7,Fpreviously committed two murders "to
OL,8,Ftake out people he was opposed to or
OL,9,Fdid not like", while Taylor had in the
OL,10,Fpast "committed serious offences in
OL,11,Fwhich he expressed a dislike of
OL,12,Fpaedophiles".
OL,14,FHe told the court Taylor went on to
OL,15,Fmurder an associate and invited a
OL,16,Fpolice officer to the prison before
OL,17,Ftrying to kill him with an improvised
OL,18,Fweapon he had hidden in his waistband.
OL,26,@oD@bOUqD@MO]rD@FOUtD@LO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FMr Pitter said Newell, who is serving
OL,7,Fa whole life order, had previously
OL,8,Fstrangled a man who murdered a child
OL,9,Fand left him in his bed, telling
OL,10,Fjurors there was "a chilling
OL,11,Fsimilarity to that and the
OL,12,Fcircumstances of Kyle Bevan's death".
OL,14,FThe prosecutor said all inmates at HMP
OL,15,FWakefield "had done very unattractive
OL,16,Fthings, offences of the most terrible
OL,17,Fkind".
OL,26,@rD@ROUtD@dO]wD@KOUyD@EO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,F"But you must not simply adopt the
OL,7,Fapproach of 'they are murderers
OL,8,Ftherefore they are guilty' or, for Mr
OL,9,FBevan, 'he's killed a child therefore
OL,10,Fhe deserved it,'" Mr Pitter said.
OL,12,F"To do either of these things would be
OL,13,Fto fail in your duty.
OL,15,F"The moral considerations are dealt
OL,16,Fwith in other places.
OL,18,F"Your job is simply to apply the law
OL,19,Fand make decisions on the facts."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]tD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FJoe Stone KC, defending Newell, told
OL,7,Fjurors that there was no CCTV in the
OL,8,Fcell, saying: "The reality is, you
OL,9,Fdon't know 100% what went on in that
OL,10,Fcell, during that five minutes.
OL,12,F"It's a tricky task for a jury to
OL,13,Fassess the evidence for these three
OL,14,Fmen when that evidential black hole is
OL,15,Fstaring you in the face.
OL,17,F"Who was the stabber? Were there
OL,18,Fstabbers in the plural? Was there
OL,19,Fsomeone who was merely in there and
OL,20,Fdid nothing?"
OL,26,@pD@OOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FHe said there was "not a scintilla of
OL,7,Fevidence" of Newell being armed, or
OL,8,Fany "blood evidence" linking him to
OL,9,Fthe attack.
OL,11,FNick Johnson KC, defending Fellows,
OL,12,Ftold jurors: "In this country you
OL,13,Fdon't just say 'those three bad men
OL,14,Fgoing into a cell, they probably did
OL,15,Fit'...Only you decide where justice
OL,16,Flies in this case."
OL,26,@nD@SOUoD@IO]pD@EOUpD@TO]tD@NOUxD@SO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FHe asked the jury to consider an
OL,7,Falternative, that Fellows went to
OL,8,FBevan's cell for another purpose and
OL,9,F"that violence erupted that he played
OL,10,Fno part in, even if he was happy to
OL,11,Fcover it up afterwards".
OL,13,FMr Johnson said Fellows was not alone
OL,14,Fin disliking child killers, or the new
OL,15,Fregime at the jail under the governor.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1781887673
OL,3,CPrisoners 'can't' explain child
OL,4,Ckiller's murder, court told
OL,6,FJeremy Dein KC, defending Taylor,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Behind the door of Kyle Bevan's
OL,8,Fcell, there is not an iota of evidence
OL,9,Fthat David Taylor stabbed Kyle Bevan,
OL,10,Fand no evidence that his presence can
OL,11,Fbe coupled, so that you are sure
OL,12,Fwith... assistance, encouragement or
OL,13,Fintent."
OL,15,FAll three defendants deny murder and
OL,16,Fthe trial continues.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@HO]
